Package com.serezk4.io.trasnfer

Class Request

java.lang.Object
com.serezk4.io.trasnfer.Request
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public final class Request extends Object implements Serializable
Represents a request containing a command, its arguments, and associated persons.

This record encapsulates all necessary data to execute a command, including the command name, optional arguments, and a list of Person objects.

Since:
1.0
